      <title>這是我的第一篇文章</title>
      <link href="/test_artical/"/>
      <url>/test_artical/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>hi~ 我是國國，身為高一的我想要深入探索程式世界，也歡迎大家與我分享、交流。</p><p>以下是 2022-4-29 更新的測試內容</p><h1 id="標題一"><a href="#標題一" class="headerlink" title="標題一"></a>標題一</h1><h2 id="標題二"><a href="#標題二" class="headerlink" title="標題二"></a>標題二</h2><h3 id="標題三"><a href="#標題三" class="headerlink" title="標題三"></a>標題三</h3><h4 id="標題四"><a href="#標題四" class="headerlink" title="標題四"></a>標題四</h4><h5 id="標題五"><a href="#標題五" class="headerlink" title="標題五"></a>標題五</h5><h6 id="標題六"><a href="#標題六" class="headerlink" title="標題六"></a>標題六</h6><hr><h2 id="渲染器的各種操作"><a href="#渲染器的各種操作" class="headerlink" title="渲染器的各種操作"></a>渲染器的各種操作</h2><p>我使用的渲染器是 <a href="https://github.com/Akilarlxh">Akilarlxh</a> 這位作者所製作的 <a href="https://github.com/Akilarlxh/hexo-butterfly-tag-plugins-plus"><code>hexo-butterfly-tag-plugins-plus</code></a></p><div class="note info no-icon flat"><p>以下內容皆為 <a href="https://github.com/Akilarlxh">Akilarlxh</a> 該作者的文本內容，複製請遵守 CC 版權！</p></div><h3 id="各種標籤塊"><a href="#各種標籤塊" class="headerlink" title="各種標籤塊"></a>各種標籤塊</h3><div class="tabs" id="note"><ul class="nav-tabs"><li class="tab active"><button type="button" data-href="#note-1">modern 樣式</button></li><li class="tab"><button type="button" data-href="#note-2">flat 樣式</button></li><li class="tab"><button type="button" data-href="#note-3">no icon 樣式</button></li></ul><div class="tab-contents"><div class="tab-item-content active" id="note-1"><div class="note modern"><p>默认 提示標籤塊</p></div><div class="note default modern"><p>default 提示標籤塊</p></div><div class="note primary modern"><p>primary 提示標籤塊</p></div><div class="note success modern"><p>success 提示標籤塊</p></div><div class="note info modern"><p>info 提示標籤塊</p></div><div class="note warning modern"><p>warning 提示標籤塊</p></div><div class="note danger modern"><p>danger 提示標籤塊</p></div><button type="button" class="tab-to-top" aria-label="scroll to top"><i class="fas fa-arrow-up"></i></button></div><div class="tab-item-content" id="note-2"><div class="note flat"><p>默认 提示標籤塊</p></div><div class="note default flat"><p>default 提示標籤塊</p></div><div class="note primary flat"><p>primary 提示標籤塊</p></div><div class="note success flat"><p>success 提示標籤塊</p></div><div class="note info flat"><p>info 提示標籤塊</p></div><div class="note warning flat"><p>warning 提示標籤塊</p></div><div class="note danger flat"><p>danger 提示標籤塊</p></div><button type="button" class="tab-to-top" aria-label="scroll to top"><i class="fas fa-arrow-up"></i></button></div><div class="tab-item-content" id="note-3"><div class="note no-icon flat"><p>默认 提示標籤塊</p></div><div class="note default no-icon flat"><p>default 提示標籤塊</p></div><div class="note primary no-icon flat"><p>primary 提示標籤塊</p></div><div class="note success no-icon flat"><p>success 提示標籤塊</p></div><div class="note info no-icon flat"><p>info 提示標籤塊</p></div><div class="note warning no-icon flat"><p>warning 提示標籤塊</p></div><div class="note danger no-icon flat"><p>danger 提示標籤塊</p></div><button type="button" class="tab-to-top" aria-label="scroll to top"><i class="fas fa-arrow-up"></i></button></div></div></div><h3 id="行內文本樣式"><a href="#行內文本樣式" class="headerlink" title="行內文本樣式"></a>行內文本樣式</h3><div class="tabs" id="文本樣式"><ul class="nav-tabs"><li class="tab active"><button type="button" data-href="#文本樣式-1">本文樣式 text</button></li><li class="tab"><button type="button" data-href="#文本樣式-2">本文色彩 span</button></li><li class="tab"><button type="button" data-href="#文本樣式-3">本文色彩 p</button></li></ul><div class="tab-contents"><div class="tab-item-content active" id="文本樣式-1"><ol><li>帶 <u>下劃線</u> 的文本</li><li>帶 <emp>著重號</emp> 的文本</li><li>帶 <wavy>波浪線</wavy> 的文本</li><li>帶 <del>刪除線</del> 的文本</li><li>鍵盤樣式的文本 <kbd>command</kbd> + <kbd>D</kbd></li><li>密碼樣式的文本：<psw>這裡沒有驗證碼</psw></li></ol><button type="button" class="tab-to-top" aria-label="scroll to top"><i class="fas fa-arrow-up"></i></button></div><div class="tab-item-content" id="文本樣式-2"><ul><li>彩色文字<br>在一段話中方便插入各種顏色的標籤，包括：<span class='p red'>紅色</span>、<span class='p yellow'>黃色</span>、<span class='p green'>綠色</span>、<span class='p cyan'>青色</span>、<span class='p blue'>藍色</span>、<span class='p gray'>灰色</span>。</li><li>超大號文字<br>文檔「開始」頁面中的標題部分就是超大號文字。<br><span class='p center logo large'>Volantis</span><br><span class='p center small'>A Wonderful Theme for Hexo</span></li></ul><button type="button" class="tab-to-top" aria-label="scroll to top"><i class="fas fa-arrow-up"></i></button></div><div class="tab-item-content" id="文本樣式-3"><ul><li>彩色文字<br>在一段話中方便插入各種顏色的標籤，包括：<p class='p red'>紅色</p>、<p class='p yellow'>黃色</p>、<p class='p green'>綠色</p>、<p class='p cyan'>青色</p>、<p class='p blue'>藍色</p>、<p class='p gray'>灰色</p>。</li><li>超大號文字<br>文檔「開始」頁面中的標題部分就是超大號文字。<p class='p center logo large'>Volantis</p><p class='p center small'>A Wonderful Theme for Hexo</p></li></ul><button type="button" class="tab-to-top" aria-label="scroll to top"><i class="fas fa-arrow-up"></i></button></div></div></div><h3 id="Checkbox"><a href="#Checkbox" class="headerlink" title="Checkbox"></a>Checkbox</h3><div class="tabs" id="checkbox"><ul class="nav-tabs"><li class="tab active"><button type="button" data-href="#checkbox-1">複選 checkbox</button></li><li class="tab"><button type="button" data-href="#checkbox-2">單選 checkbox</button></li></ul><div class="tab-contents"><div class="tab-item-content active" id="checkbox-1"><div class='checkbox'><input type="checkbox" />            <p>純文本測試</p>            </div><div class='checkbox checked'><input type="checkbox" checked="checked"/>            <p>支持簡單的 <a href="https://guides.github.com/features/mastering-markdown/">markdown</a> 語法</p>            </div><div class='checkbox red'><input type="checkbox" />            <p>支持自定義顏色</p>            </div><div class='checkbox green checked'><input type="checkbox" checked="checked"/>            <p>綠色 + 默認選中</p>            </div><div class='checkbox yellow checked'><input type="checkbox" checked="checked"/>            <p>黃色 + 默認選中</p>            </div><div class='checkbox cyan checked'><input type="checkbox" checked="checked"/>            <p>青色 + 默認選中</p>            </div><div class='checkbox blue checked'><input type="checkbox" checked="checked"/>            <p>藍色 + 默認選中</p>            </div><div class='checkbox plus green checked'><input type="checkbox" checked="checked"/>            <p>增加</p>            </div><div class='checkbox minus yellow checked'><input type="checkbox" checked="checked"/>            <p>減少</p>            </div><div class='checkbox times red checked'><input type="checkbox" checked="checked"/>            <p>叉</p>            </div><button type="button" class="tab-to-top" aria-label="scroll to top"><i class="fas fa-arrow-up"></i></button></div><div class="tab-item-content" id="checkbox-2"><div class='checkbox'><input type="radio" />            <p>純文本測試</p>            </div><div class='checkbox checked'><input type="radio" checked="checked"/>            <p>支持簡單的 <a href="https://guides.github.com/features/mastering-markdown/">markdown</a> 語法</p>            </div><div class='checkbox red'><input type="radio" />            <p>支持自定義顏色</p>            </div><div class='checkbox green'><input type="radio" />            <p>綠色</p>            </div><div class='checkbox yellow'><input type="radio" />            <p>黃色</p>            </div><div class='checkbox cyan'><input type="radio" />            <p>青色</p>            </div><div class='checkbox blue'><input type="radio" />            <p>藍色</p>            </div><button type="button" class="tab-to-top" aria-label="scroll to top"><i class="fas fa-arrow-up"></i></button></div></div></div><h3 id="摺疊"><a href="#摺疊" class="headerlink" title="摺疊"></a>摺疊</h3><details class="folding-tag" cyan open><summary> 查看默認打開的折疊框 </summary>              <div class='content'>              <p>這是一個默認打開的折疊框。</p>              </div>            </details><h3 id="github-卡片"><a href="#github-卡片" class="headerlink" title="github 卡片"></a>github 卡片</h3><a class="ghcard" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer" href="https://github.com/huangmayor0905">